  "texts": [
    "ConclusionWe present a follow up analysis comparing the accuracy and comprehensiveness of responses from GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 to questions related to bariatric surgery.",
    "In terms of accuracy, our results show a largely uniform performance between the two models with a significant majority (88.1%) of responses graded as having similar accuracy.",
    "These findings may suggest a degree of stability and reliability among the core algorithms when it comes to the generation of accurate responses.",
    "It is important to note that both models have been undergoing continuous refinement and updating, which may explain this comparability in performance.",
    "A more striking differentiation was observed when examining the comprehensiveness of responses."
  ],
